<dl><dt>Con</dt></dl>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20060127011150/http://www.monergism.com/thethreshold/articles/topic/definiteatonement.html">Articles on Definite Atonement</a> at Monergism.com</li>
