<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://reformedperspectives.org/search.asp/keyword/THsal/category/th#ra_mclaughlin">"Limited Atonement"</a>, a series of articles by Ra McLaughlin</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ccel.org/ccel/boettner/predest.iv.iv.html">"Limited Atonement"</a>, chapter 12 from <i>The Reformed Doctrine of Predestination</i> by Loraine Boettner</li>
